                <div class="section" id="contribute-to-the-core">
                    <span id="start-coredev"></span>
                    <h2>Contribute to the core<a class="headerlink" href="#contribute-to-the-core"
                                                 title="Permalink to this headline">¶</a></h2>
                    <p>The “Core contribution guide” contains information for creating core
                        patches:</p>
                    <ul class="simple">
                        <li><a class="reference external"
                               href="m/typo3/guide-contributionworkflow/master/en-us/BugfixingAZ/Index.html#quickstart-create-a-patch"
                               title="(in TYPO3 Contribution Guide - Core Development v1.0)"><span
                                        class="xref std std-ref">Create a patch</span></a></li>
                        <li><a class="reference external"
                               href="m/typo3/guide-contributionworkflow/master/en-us/Appendix/CommitMessage.html#commitmessage"
                               title="(in TYPO3 Contribution Guide - Core Development v1.0)"><span
                                        class="xref std std-ref">Commit message rules</span></a></li>
                        <li><a class="reference external"
                               href="m/typo3/guide-contributionworkflow/master/en-us/Appendix/SettingUpTypo3Ddev.html#ddev"
                               title="(in TYPO3 Contribution Guide - Core Development v1.0)"><span
                                        class="xref std std-ref">Setup an installation with DDEV</span></a></li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>But contributions aren’t just about writing patches. You can contribute
                        in numerous other ways, including</p>
                    <ul class="simple">
                        <li><a class="reference external"
                               href="m/typo3/guide-contributionworkflow/master/en-us/ReportingAnIssue/Index.html#forge-index"
                               title="(in TYPO3 Contribution Guide - Core Development v1.0)"><span
